div.p:
The projections of the first class of bodies will consist of straight lines;
                    those of the second class, of curved as well as straight lines; and those of the
                    third class, of curved lines only.

A piece of work glued up in thicknesses should be very well done; but it too
                    often happens that the joints are visible, irregular, and in some places open;
                    therefore other methods have been tried.
